com.stormpath.sdk.query
Interface StringExpressionFactory

public interface StringExpressionFactory

An StringExpressionFactory creates String conditions (equals, startsWith, etc) for specific resource properties.

Since:
0.8

Method Summary

          Returns a new case-insensitive like expression indicating the specified value should be contained anywhere in the property value.
